### Register a new staff user
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "staff1@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "fullName": "Jane Staff",
  "role": "STAFF"
}

### Login
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "staff1@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}